<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٣١١٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو بَكْرٍ قَالَ:</span> ثنا وَكِيعٌ، عَنْ حَسَنِ بْنِ صَالِحٍ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ جَعْفَرًا عَنْ الْمِلْحِ لِلْمُحْرِمِ <span class="c2">«فَكَرِهَهُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>